{"title": "ffuf", "source": "enum", "source_label": "Enumeration", "path": "ffuf", "html": "<h1 id=\"ffuf\">ffuf</h1>\n<h2 id=\"directory-fuzzing\">Directory Fuzzing</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Basic directory brute force</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># With extensions</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-e<span class=\"w\"> </span>.php,.html,.txt,.bak,.old,.zip,.tar.gz\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Specific extensions</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ.php<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Output to file</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>results.json<span class=\"w\"> </span>-of<span class=\"w\"> </span>json\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Rate limited</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-rate<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">50</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># With threads</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">50</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># With proxy (Burp)</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-x<span class=\"w\"> </span>http://127.0.0.1:8080\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Ignore SSL errors</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Follow redirects</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-r\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Custom timeout</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-timeout<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"filter-options\">Filter Options</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Filter by HTTP status code (hide 404)</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Filter multiple codes</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>,403,500\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Match only specific codes</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-mc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span>,301,302\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Filter by response size (bytes)</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fs<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1234</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Filter by number of words</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fw<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Filter by number of lines</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fl<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">42</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Filter by response time (ms)</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-ft<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">100</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Match by size</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-ms<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1234</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Match by words</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-mw<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">50</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Match by regex</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-mr<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;admin|panel|dashboard&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"vhost-fuzzing\">VHost Fuzzing</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># VHost enumeration</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Host: FUZZ.&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-fs<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1234</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># With different base response size (filter known size)</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>http://&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Host: FUZZ.&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fs<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">0</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># HTTPS vhost</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>https://&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Host: FUZZ.&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># VHost with specific match</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>http://&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Host: FUZZ.&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-mc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span>,301,302,400\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Find first valid vhost size then filter</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>http://&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Host: test.&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/dev/null<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\"># get baseline size</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>http://&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Host: FUZZ.&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fs<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;baseline_size&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"subdomain-fuzzing\">Subdomain Fuzzing</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># DNS subdomain fuzzing</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>http://FUZZ.&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Filter by size</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>http://FUZZ.&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fs<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-fc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># With SSL</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>https://FUZZ.&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Custom resolver</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>http://FUZZ.&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Host: FUZZ.&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"get-parameter-fuzzing\">GET Parameter Fuzzing</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Fuzz GET parameter value</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=FUZZ&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Fuzz parameter name</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?FUZZ=test&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/burp-parameter-names.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Multiple GET params</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?page=FUZZ&amp;id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Filter default response</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=FUZZ&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fs<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1234</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># LFI fuzzing</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?file=FUZZ&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Fuzzing/LFI/LFI-Jhaddix.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fs<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">0</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SQLi parameter</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=FUZZ&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Fuzzing/SQLi/Generic-SQLi.txt\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"post-parameter-fuzzing\">POST Parameter Fuzzing</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># POST body fuzzing</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-X<span class=\"w\"> </span>POST<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;username=FUZZ&amp;password=test&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># POST with JSON body</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-X<span class=\"w\"> </span>POST<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Content-Type: application/json&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;{&quot;username&quot;:&quot;FUZZ&quot;,&quot;password&quot;:&quot;test&quot;}&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Fuzz POST parameter name</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-X<span class=\"w\"> </span>POST<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;FUZZ=test&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/burp-parameter-names.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Password spray</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-X<span class=\"w\"> </span>POST<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;username=&lt;username&gt;&amp;password=FUZZ&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-mc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">302</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># JSON API fuzzing</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/api/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-X<span class=\"w\"> </span>POST<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Content-Type: application/json&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;{}&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"recursive-fuzzing\">Recursive Fuzzing</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Recursive directory fuzzing</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-recursion\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Recursive with depth limit</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-recursion<span class=\"w\"> </span>-recursion-depth<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Recursive with extensions</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-recursion<span class=\"w\"> </span>-recursion-depth<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-e<span class=\"w\"> </span>.php,.html,.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Recursive with filter</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-recursion<span class=\"w\"> </span>-recursion-depth<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-fc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>,403\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"authentication\">Authentication</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Basic authentication</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Bearer token</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Authorization: Bearer &lt;password&gt;&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Cookie authentication</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Cookie: session=&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Multiple headers</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Authorization: Bearer &lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;X-Api-Key: abc123&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Accept: application/json&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># API key in parameter</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ?api_key=&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"multiple-injection-points-multiple-wordlists\">Multiple Injection Points (Multiple Wordlists)</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Two FUZZ points with two wordlists</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ1/FUZ2Z<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>users.txt:FUZZ1<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;:FUZ2Z\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Username + password brute force</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/login<span class=\"w\"> </span>-X<span class=\"w\"> </span>POST<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;user=FUZZ&amp;pass=FUZ2Z&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Usernames/top-usernames-shortlist.txt:FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Passwords/Common-Credentials/10-million-password-list-top-100.txt:FUZ2Z<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-fc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Credential stuffing from colon-delimited list</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/login<span class=\"w\"> </span>-X<span class=\"w\"> </span>POST<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;user=FUZZ&amp;pass=FUZ2Z&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>creds.txt:FUZZ:FUZ2Z<span class=\"w\"> </span>-ic\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"api-fuzzing\">API Fuzzing</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># REST API endpoint discovery</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/api/v1/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/api/api-endpoints.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-mc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span>,201,204,400,401,403\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># API version fuzzing</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/api/FUZZ/users<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-mc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span>,201\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># GraphQL introspection endpoint</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-mr<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;graphql|__schema&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># API parameter fuzzing with JSON</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/api/users<span class=\"w\"> </span>-X<span class=\"w\"> </span>POST<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Content-Type: application/json&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;{&quot;FUZZ&quot;:&quot;test&quot;}&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/burp-parameter-names.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-mr<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&quot;id&quot;:|&quot;user&quot;:|&quot;success&quot;&#39;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># IDOR enumeration</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/api/users/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;<span class=\"o\">(</span>seq<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1000</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-mc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Method fuzzing</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/api/users<span class=\"w\"> </span>-X<span class=\"w\"> </span>FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;{}&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">echo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-e<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;GET\\nPOST\\nPUT\\nPATCH\\nDELETE\\nOPTIONS\\nHEAD&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-mc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span>,201,204\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"output-formats\">Output Formats</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># JSON output</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>output.json<span class=\"w\"> </span>-of<span class=\"w\"> </span>json\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># CSV output</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>output.csv<span class=\"w\"> </span>-of<span class=\"w\"> </span>csv\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># HTML report</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>report.html<span class=\"w\"> </span>-of<span class=\"w\"> </span>html\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># eJSONLines format</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>output.ejson<span class=\"w\"> </span>-of<span class=\"w\"> </span>ejson\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Markdown</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>output.md<span class=\"w\"> </span>-of<span class=\"w\"> </span>md\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># All formats (use multiple -o)</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>output.json<span class=\"w\"> </span>-of<span class=\"w\"> </span>json<span class=\"w\"> </span>-of<span class=\"w\"> </span>md<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>output.md\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"common-wordlists\">Common Wordlists</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># SecLists paths</span>\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/directory-list-2.3-small.txt\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-directories.txt\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-files.txt\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/common.txt\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt\n/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-20000.txt\n/usr/share/seclists/Fuzzing/LFI/LFI-Jhaddix.txt\n/usr/share/seclists/Fuzzing/SQLi/Generic-SQLi.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Dirbuster wordlists (sometimes better for specific apps)</span>\n/usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"practical-one-liners\">Practical One-Liners</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Fast initial recon</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-directories.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">100</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-c\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># PHP app</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-directories.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-e<span class=\"w\"> </span>.php,.html,.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># API discovery</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/api/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/common.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-mc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span>,201,204,400,401,403,405\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Backup file hunt</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-files.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-e<span class=\"w\"> </span>.bak,.old,.orig,.swp,.~<span class=\"w\"> </span>-mc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Auto-calibrate filter (send request with random path first)</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-ac\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Silent mode (no banner, only results)</span>\nffuf<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-s<span class=\"w\"> </span>-fc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "ffuf Directory Fuzzing # Basic directory brute force ffuf -u &lt;url&gt;/FUZZ -w &lt;wordlist&gt; # With extensions ffuf -u &lt;url&gt;/FUZZ -w &lt;wordlist&gt; -e .php,.html,.txt,.bak,.old,.zip,.tar.", "tags": []}